ng\" rel=\"lightbox-0\"><img src=\"https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/logo-512x512-100x100.png\" alt=\"logo-512x512\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" class=\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-699\" srcset=\"https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/logo-512x512-100x100.png 100w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/logo-512x512-300x300.png 300w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/logo-512x512-150x150.png 150w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/logo-512x512-200x200.png 200w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/logo-512x512-450x450.png 450w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/logo-512x512-90x90.png 90w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/logo-512x512.png 512w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 100px) 100vw, 100px\" /></a>A small update fixing a bunch of things including stats exports and some statistics views. Based on user feedback and popular countries (Where I have more than average sales) those currencies have been added as well, for transactions.</p>\n<h2>Changes</h2>\n<div class=\"shortcode-unorderedlist arrow\">\n<ul>\n<li>[new] More currencies to use</li>\n<li>[fix] Dashboard notifications can not be turned off</li>\n<li>[fix] Todays view of group stats</li>\n<li>[fix] Group and Advert stats export works again</li>\n<li>[change] Export file names more web-friendly</li>\n</ul>\n<p></div>\n\n<h2>Green grass</h2>\n<p>Sometimes it&#8217;s just nice to look down at the grass and see whatever is in there.<br />\n<a href=\"https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/green-grass.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox-1\"><img src=\"https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/green-grass-768x1024.jpg\" alt=\"green-grass\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-21098\" srcset=\"https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/green-grass-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/green-grass-225x300.jpg 225w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/green-grass.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" /></a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:75:\"https://ajdg.solutions/2016/10/24/adrotate-pro-4-1-3-tweaks-and-fixes/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:38:\"AdRotate 3.16.1 – Maintenance update\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:69:\"https://ajdg.solutions/2016/10/12/adrotate-3-16-1-maintenance-update/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:77:\"https://ajdg.solutions/2016/10/12/adrotate-3-16-1-maintenance-update/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 12 Oct 2016 06:00:10 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:7:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"AdRotate Plugin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"