go-512x512-100x100.png\" alt=\"logo-512x512\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" class=\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-699\" srcset=\"https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/logo-512x512-100x100.png 100w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/logo-512x512-300x300.png 300w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/logo-512x512-150x150.png 150w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/logo-512x512-200x200.png 200w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/logo-512x512-450x450.png 450w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/logo-512x512-90x90.png 90w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/logo-512x512.png 512w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 100px) 100vw, 100px\" /></a>Fixed a long standing bug where status messages taken on certain actions such as deleting or renewing adverts. The right message is now displayed.</p>\n<h2>Changes</h2>\n<div class=\"shortcode-unorderedlist arrow\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>[fix] Advert status messages not showing the right message</li>\n<li>[fix] Clicktracking not always working when HTML is uppercase</li>\n</ul>\n<p></div>\n\n<h2>A million trees</h2>\n<p>To stop erosion of the land people planted a huge mahogany forest on Bohol.<br />\n<a href=\"https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/manmade-forest.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox-1\"><img src=\"https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/manmade-forest-768x1024.jpg\" alt=\"manmade-forest\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-20659\" srcset=\"https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/manmade-forest-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/manmade-forest-225x300.jpg 225w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/manmade-forest.jpg 960w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" /></a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:1