ads/2014/06/logo-512x512-150x150.png 150w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/logo-512x512-200x200.png 200w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/logo-512x512-450x450.png 450w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/logo-512x512-90x90.png 90w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/logo-512x512.png 512w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 100px) 100vw, 100px\" /></a>Maintenance update fixing a whole bunch of quirks and items related to advertisers. Some changes made on user feedback, a lot of fixes and tweaks also based on user feedback. Advertiser features should now work more smooth and logical.</p>\n<h2>Changes</h2>\n<div class=\"shortcode-unorderedlist arrow\">\n<ul>\n<li>[new] Australian Dollars for transactions</li>\n<li>[new] Fallback groups hidden for advertisers</li>\n<li>[fix] No longer list empty adverts in transactions menu</li>\n<li>[fix] Wrong table prefix for new listing adverts in new transactions</li>\n<li>[fix] Better widget output for W3 Total Cache</li>\n<li>[fix] Todays stats for single adverts displaying the wrong numbers</li>\n<li>[fix] Undefined notices on Advertiser pages</li>\n<li>[fix] Undefined notices on User creation page</li>\n<li>[fix] Unpaid adverts showing as active when editing groups</li>\n<li>[fix] Unpaid adverts still showing for some groups</li>\n</ul>\n<p></div>\n\n<h2>Travelpartner</h2>\n<p>Recently I found a great girlfriend who wants to travel with me <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/2/72x72/1f642.png\" alt=\"?\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/apple.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox-1\"><img src=\"https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/apple-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"apple\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-20657\" srcset=\"https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/apple-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/apple-300x225.jpg 300w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/apple-768x576.jpg 768w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/apple.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:78:\"https://ajdg.solutions/2016/10/11/adrotate-pro-4-1-2-bugfixes-and-tweaks/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"One year in the Philippines, 20% off on all plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:84:\"https://ajdg.solutions/2016/09/30/one-year-in-the-philippines-20-off-on-all-plugins/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 30 Sep 2016 06:14:53 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"https://ajdg.solutions/?p=19037\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:362:\"I&#8217;m in the Philippines for one year this week. That&#8217;s a milestone&#8230; I think it&#8217;s a milestone ? So, reason to celebrate. Grab your copy of AdRotate Pro, Omnikassa for WooCommerce or Merchant E-Solutions for WooCommerce at a discounted price of 20% off this week. Promo details Valid: September 30 through October 7, 2016 (GMT+8 [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"Arnan\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2216:\"<p><a href=\"https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/ajdg-sale.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox-0\"><img src=\"https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/ajdg-sale-1024x402.jpg\" alt=\"ajdg-sale\" width=\"1024\" height=\"402\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-19034\" srcset=\"https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/ajdg-sale-1024x402.jpg 1024w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/ajdg-sale-300x118.jpg 300w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/ajdg-sale-768x302.jpg 768w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/ajdg-sale.jpg 1426w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></p>\n<p>I&#8217;m in the Philippines for one year this week. That&#8217;s a milestone&#8230; I think it&#8217;s a milestone <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/2/72x72/1f642.png\" alt=\"?\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> So, reason to celebrate. Grab your copy of AdRotate Pro, Omnikassa for WooCommerce or Merchant E-Solutions for WooCommerce at a discounted price of 20% off this week.</p>\n<h2>Promo details</h2>\n<p><strong>Valid:</strong> September 30 through October 7, 2016 (GMT+8 timezone, that&#8217;s South East Asia).<br />\n<strong>Coupon Code:</strong> ONEYEARPH<br />\n<strong>Discount:</strong> 20% on all plugins/licenses.</p>\n<h2>Cultureshock</h2>\n<p>You know, that stupid feeling when everything is wondrous, tiring, amazing and strange. But you don&#8217;t really care while you totally should? Yea, culture shock when I arrived in the Philippines. Or maybe it was the heat. Anyway, this is what my backpack looked like a year ago.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/fresh-of-the-boat.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox-1\"><img src=\"https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/fresh-of-the-boat-768x1024.jpg\" alt=\"fresh-of-the-boat\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-19040\" srcset=\"https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/fresh-of-the-boat-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/fresh-of-the-boat-225x300.jpg 225w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/fresh-of-the-boat.jpg 960w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" /></a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"AdRotate Pro 4.1.1 – Bugfixes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:62:\"https://ajdg.solutions/2016/09/28/adrotate-pro-4-1-1-bugfixes/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1