 &#8220;before&#8221; and &#8220;after&#8221; fields we&#8217;re not properly [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"Arnan\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2760:\"<p><a href=\"https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/logo-512x512.png\" rel=\"lightbox-0\"><img src=\"https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/logo-512x512-100x100.png\" alt=\"logo-512x512\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" class=\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-699\" srcset=\"https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/logo-512x512-100x100.png 100w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/logo-512x512-300x300.png 300w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/logo-512x512-150x150.png 150w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/logo-512x512-200x200.png 200w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/logo-512x512-450x450.png 450w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/logo-512x512-90x90.png 90w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/logo-512x512.png 512w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 100px) 100vw, 100px\" /></a>A whole bunch of bugfixes for the new features and the overall dashboard.<br />\nWidgets do now work again, settings can be saved and there is actual output.</p>\n<p>I couldn&#8217;t reproduce or find a proper cause for garbled output when you use W3 Total Cache. But the new widget &#8220;before&#8221; and &#8220;after&#8221; fields we&#8217;re not properly hooked into the fragmented caching feature so that should fix that. Some quirks on the dashboard are resolved for a smoother experience and statistics overview.</p>\n<h2>Changes</h2>\n<div class=\"shortcode-unorderedlist arrow\">\n<ul>\n<li>[fix] Better colour indicators for adverts in various dashboards</li>\n<li>[fix] Undefined notices in widgets</li>\n<li>[fix] Caching output not always working</li>\n<li>[fix] Widgets not always keeping settings when saving</li>\n<li>[fix] Widgets not following network setting for some people</li>\n<li>[fix] Stats display giving errors when there are no stats</li>\n<li>[fix] Cleaner statistics display for clicks/impressions/ctr</li>\n</ul>\n<p></div>\n\n<h2>Immigration</h2>\n<p>Being a traveller or Digital Nomad lowers certain costs, but inflates others. Prepare for a lot of Immigration fees! </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/puerto-galera-boi.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox-1\"><img src=\"https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/puerto-galera-boi-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"puerto-galera-boi\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-20211\" srcset=\"https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/puerto-galera-boi-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/puerto-galera-boi-300x225.jpg 300w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/puerto-galera-boi-768x576.jpg 768w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/puerto-galera-boi.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:67:\"https://ajdg.solutions/2016/09/28/adrotate-pro-4-1-1-bugfixes/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				